Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.49,0:06:37.66,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{What's this supposed to be?}Cái quái gì đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.66,0:06:39.49,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{Just what it looks like. A scale.}Thì là cái cân chứ gì.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.49,0:06:41.42,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{Hop on, Paula.}Lên đi Paula.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.42,0:06:42.70,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,{Okay...}Vâng...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.38,0:06:49.19,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,{It says 36 kilos. So what's the big idea?}36 kí. Có vấn đề gì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.19,0:06:52.14,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{Now try reducing your weight to zero.}Giờ thì đưa cân nặng về 0 xem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.98,0:06:54.51,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,{Like this?}Thế này á?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.72,0:07:00.85,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{Well, that explains how you're so good \Nat moving without making a sound.}Không hổ danh bậc thầy ẩn nấp.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.85,0:07:01.35,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnArial\fs12\b1\shad0\c&H351AA6&\3c&HECF7FC&\pos(525.81,58.571)}{Fast Forward Explanation in Progress}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.85,0:07:02.86,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{Doing this allows you \Nto move silently and swiftly,}Hạ cân nặng sẽ giúp di chuyển nhẹ nhàng và nhanh gọn,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.87,0:07:02.35,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnArial\fs12\b1\shad0\c&H351AA6&\3c&HECF7FC&\pos(525.81,58.571)}{Fast Forward Explanation in Progress}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.86,0:07:03.73,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{as well as scale walls and ceilings.}dù là tường hay trần nhà.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.87,0:07:03.35,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnArial\fs12\b1\shad0\c&H351AA6&\3c&HECF7FC&\pos(525.81,58.571)}{Fast Forward Explanation in Progress}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.73,0:07:05.65,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{Now, want to land heavier attacks?\NJust make yourself heavier instead!}Vậy giờ nếu muốn tăng sức nặng cho cú \Nđấm thì chỉ cần tăng cân nặng là được.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.87,0:07:04.35,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnArial\fs12\b1\shad0\c&H351AA6&\3c&HECF7FC&\pos(525.81,58.571)}{Fast Forward Explanation in Progress}
