Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.01,0:07:12.76,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{Easy as pie.}Dễ như ăn bánh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.76,0:07:14.76,Italics,Narr,0,0,0,,{All Idaten are capable of \Nmaking themselves lighter.}Tất cả Idaten đều có thể làm cơ thể nhẹ hơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.88,0:07:13.36,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnArial\fs12\b1\shad0\c&H351AA6&\3c&HECF7FC&\pos(525.81,58.571)}{Fast Forward Explanation in Progress}
